# Home Lab-Setup for RHCSA 

This repository documents my personal RHCSA/RHCE home lab built with RHEL 10 on Hyper-V Manager. The lab is designed for hands-on, scenario-based practice to strengthen Linux system administration skills and develop Ansible automation experience in preparation for the RHCSA v9/10 and RHCE exams.

